---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../site';
---

<Base lang="en" title="About — Almohannad Alsbeai" altPath="/about" current="/en/about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="deck" data-pagefind-body>
      <article class="fcard fcard--cover">
        <img class="cover-avatar" src="/images/avatar.jpg" alt="Almohannad Alsbeai" width="84" height="84" />
        <h1>Beyond the Bio</h1>
        <p>A few cards on the person behind the work — Almohannad Alsbeai.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <h2>Named After a Sword</h2>
        <div class="fc-term"><span class="term">Almohannad · المُهنَّد</span><span class="pos">[noun]</span></div>
        <p class="fc-pron">Pronunciation: /al.mu'han.nad/</p>
        <p>A high-quality, finely crafted sword made from Indian steel — famed for its strength, sharpness, and craftsmanship.</p>
        <p><strong>TL;DR:</strong> a symbol of power, precision, and honor in Arabic culture. In Islamic tradition it's associated with valor and righteous warriors, and appears as a poetic epithet in classical Arabic literature.</p>
        <p class="fcard-note">Call me Mohannad — drop the "Al," it's simpler. Or, if you prefer tradition, Abu Rand works too.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <h2>Not Loud, but Solid</h2>
        <p class="fcard-lead">I value structure, responsibility, and quiet strength.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>I value clarity, stability, and doing things right over doing them fast.</li>
          <li>I thrive in trust-based environments where respect and reliability matter.</li>
          <li>I think things through before speaking — measured, not passive.</li>
          <li>I lean introverted, but I care deeply about meaningful collaboration.</li>
          <li>I lead with authenticity, calm, and empathy — not with volume.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="fcard-note">In short: I'm the person you can count on. Quietly present. Consistently dependable.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <h2>My Values, My Compass</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Responsibility:</strong> I own my actions and their impact; others can rely on me.</li>
          <li><strong>Empathy:</strong> I listen to understand and lead with emotional awareness.</li>
          <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> I do what's right and communicate honestly.</li>
          <li><strong>Self-discipline:</strong> I value self-control, structure, and intentional growth.</li>
          <li><strong>Wisdom:</strong> I aim for thoughtful decisions and learn from experience.</li>
          <li><strong>Independence:</strong> I think independently, stay grounded, and stay true to myself.</li>
          <li><strong>Meaning:</strong> I seek meaningful work, not just results.</li>
        </ol>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">4</span>
        <h2>Life Beyond Work</h2>
        <p>While I'm focused and structured at work, at home I lead with my heart.</p>
        <p><strong>My family are my reason, my joy, and my greatest support.</strong></p>
        <p>They remind me that while work matters, love is everything. 🤍</p>
        <p>A proud father of three: Rand (2010), Ward (2012), and Zaid (2018).</p>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">5</span>
        <h2>Fuel for My Free Time</h2>
        <p class="fcard-lead">I believe what we love in our free time says as much about us as our job titles. These are mine:</p>
        <ul class="plain">
          <li>📚 Reading — my way to live countless lives.</li>
          <li>📝 Writing — to structure my thoughts and find clarity.</li>
          <li>🍳 Cooking — to unwind, and to show care for others.</li>
          <li>🏓 Ping pong — pretty sharp: fast hands, tricky spins.</li>
          <li>🎾 Padel — still a newbie, but loving the learning.</li>
          <li>☕ Coffee — brewing is a ritual I love.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">6</span>
        <h2>A Journey, Not a Destination</h2>
        <p class="fcard-lead">Over 18 years, I've worked at 9 companies — each shaped my growth in a distinct way.</p>
        <p>💡 I stay as long as I can add value or gain value. When neither is possible, I move on.</p>
        <ol class="companies">
          <li><strong>FedEx:</strong> global logistics and courier, known for speed and reliability.</li>
          <li><strong>Synovate:</strong> a global marketing-research agency, later acquired by Ipsos.</li>
          <li><strong>Ipsos:</strong> a leading global market-research firm.</li>
          <li><strong>Elm:</strong> a semi-government provider of digital and e-government solutions.</li>
          <li><strong>Al Rajhi Bank:</strong> the largest Islamic bank; retail and corporate banking.</li>
          <li><strong>Saudi Exports:</strong> a government authority promoting non-oil exports.</li>
          <li><strong>Shawarmer:</strong> the largest shawarma QSR chain in Saudi Arabia.</li>
          <li><strong>Tweeq:</strong> a fintech startup (EMI license), acquired by Tabby.</li>
          <li><strong>Rewaa:</strong> fast-growing SaaS for inventory, POS, and accounting.</li>
        </ol>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard">
        <span class="fcard-num" aria-hidden="true">7</span>
        <h2>Here to Elevate, Not Evaluate</h2>
        <p class="fcard-lead">When I join a team, I'm here to elevate, not evaluate — to help it stand out through exceptional CX. How I work:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Assess CX maturity and build a practical roadmap for improvement.</li>
          <li>Listen and ask questions to find opportunities — never to criticize.</li>
          <li>Develop the right methodologies to measure what truly matters.</li>
          <li>Redesign customer journeys so we keep the promises we've made.</li>
          <li>Strengthen the culture until exceptional CX becomes the standard.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="fcard-note"><strong>My promise:</strong> I build on what's already there. My role is to help raise the bar together — openly, respectfully, and transparently.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="fcard fcard--cover">
        <p>Want to talk? Find me on <a href={SITE.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <div style="height: 2rem"></div>
  </div>
</Base>
